723455f-a.title: Manhattan: Suffolk Street - Rivington Street
723455f-a.text:
122-118 Suffolk Street, at, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner
of Rivington Street. Also shown is Rivington Street, at and adjoining
the S.E. corner of Suffolk Street.
About 1915.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

722988f-c.title: Manhattan: Rivington Street - Suffolk Street
722988f-c.text:
Rivington Street, north side, west from Suffolk St.,
showing a cleared site at the corner surrounded by tenements.
Views 2 and 3 are limited to this feature, where formerly
stood two tenements that bore No's. 146 and 144 Rivington St.
View 1 May 12, 1939
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
Views 2 and 3: 1937
